        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"519774\">Duyal Yolcu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/253118-theory.3A-probability/topic/.22quasi-knowledge.22.20of.20an.20agent.20as.20an.20R-algebra.20and.20convex.20opt/near/292599003\">said</a>:<br>\n(I updated the text, it now develops a concrete example in section 6 where I write down some representative matrices considering an agent observing biased coin flips, also fixed a typo and missing matrix transposes).</p>",
